public class CentroidCosineSimilarity<U>
extends BipartiteRecommender<U>
Recommender. Builds a centroid for each user in the network, using the vectors of the followed users. The score is then computed as the cosine similarity of those centroids.
Author:
Javier Sanz-Cruzado (javier.sanz-cruzado@uam.es), Pablo Castells (pablo.castells@uam.es)
